 monitor listen;z;rc;con;event;data;ns;i;cid;uid;type;tkn;fn;m;removed;done;cb;port;host;json
 ‚ćĚ While there is anything in the queue, monitor Conga messages
 ‚ćĚ and release functions waiting on ‚éēTPUT

 listening‚Üźlisten
 :While listening‚ą®0‚Č†‚ČĘqueue
     :If 0=‚äÉz‚ÜźiConga.Wait'.' 5000
         (rc con event data)‚Üź4‚ÜĎz

         :Select event
         :Case 'Timeout' ‚čĄ :Continue
         :Case 'Connect'
             (host port)‚Üź(2‚äÉiConga.GetProp con'PeerAddr')[2 4]
             cid‚ÜźAddConnection con((-':'‚ć≥‚ć®‚ĆĹhost)‚Üďhost)port
             Handshake&cid ‚ćĚ Handshake must run on another thread

         :Case 'Block'
             :If (‚ČĘconns)<i‚Üźconns[;2]‚ć≥‚äācon
                 Log'*** Message received on unexpected connection'
                 Log'===> ',,‚ćēz
                 :Continue
             :Else
                 cid‚Üźconns[i;1]
             :EndIf

             uid‚Üź0
             :Trap 6 11 ‚ćĚ Might be handshake and not JSON data, or JSON data with no UID
                 json‚Üź'UTF-8' ‚éēUCS ‚éēUCS data
                 data‚Üź0 ‚éēJSON json
                 Log 'GET ',(‚ćēcid),': ',json
                 tkn‚Üź'uid'GetToken uid‚Üź2‚äÉ2‚äÉ‚éēVFI data[2].UID
             :Else
                 tkn‚Üź'cid'GetToken cid
             :EndTrap

             :Hold 'hmon'
                 cb‚Üź0
                 :If 'UserMessage'‚Č°‚äÉdata
                     Log 'User Message from ',(‚ćēcid),': ',(2‚äÉdata).Message
                 :ElseIf (‚ČĘqueue)<i‚Üźqueue[;1 2]‚ć≥cid uid
                     Log'*** Unexpected message received'
                     Log'===> ',,‚ćēz
