                 :ElseIf cb‚Üź(0‚Č†‚ČĘfn‚Üź‚äÉqueue[i;3])‚ąß'Subscribed'‚ČĘ‚äÉdata ‚ćĚ Callback fn (ignore for "Subscribe" call)
                     (‚ćéfn)&data            ‚ćĚ Run it in a separate thread
                 :EndIf

                 :If done‚Üź~(0 2‚ąä‚ć®10|‚éēDR)data    ‚ćĚ If namespace, check polling state
                     done‚Üźdata[2].{6::0 ‚čĄ Interval=0}‚ć¨  ‚ćĚ Polling done
                 :EndIf
